cts the pulsations of\nthe only known variable low-mass white dwarf (SDSS J184037.78+642312.3), and\nalso predicts both $g$- and $p$-mode pulsational instabilities in a significant\nnumber of known low-mass and ELM white dwarfs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 23 Sep 2012 20:37:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
